'''滑結樂團'''（{{lang-en|'''Slipknot'''}}）是來自美國[[愛荷華州|愛荷華州]][[狄蒙|狄蒙]]的金屬樂團<ref name="books">{{cite news |language= 中文 |url= http://www.books.com.tw/products/0020163190 |title= Slipknot / Antennas To Hell (2CD+1DVD) |publisher= [[博客來|博客來]] |accessdate= 2016-09-15 |archive-date= 2019-05-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190524154441/https://www.books.com.tw/products/0020163190 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。成立於1995年。經過早期的幾次成員變化，目前樂團的固定陣容為九名成員。創團貝斯手於2010年逝世<ref name="books"/>。2013年創團鼓手因身體問題而離團。2014年加入新任貝斯手與鼓手。2019年，於1998年加入的打擊樂手因金錢與法律糾紛而退團。其他六名成員則是在首張專輯發行之前，就一直維持到現在。

特色是醒目的驚悚面具，歇斯底里、極具侵略性的音樂風格，以及充滿暴戾、瘋狂和混亂的現場演出<ref name="books"/><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/slipknot-mn0000750742 |title=Slipknot |publisher=[[AllMusic|AllMusic]] |accessdate=2013-02-04 |archive-date=2013-06-15 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HOVoZyvv?url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/slipknot-mn0000750742 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books/about/Slipknot.html?id=67tBhuvwLuYC |title=Slipknot: Unmasked |publisher=Joel McIver |date=2001-12-01 |access-date=2016-09-15 |archive-date=2019-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812095121/https://books.google.com/books/about/Slipknot.html%3Fid%3D67tBhuvwLuYC |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1999年發行首張同名專輯後迅速成名，登上美國告示牌潛力專輯榜第1名<ref name="books"/>。2001年第二張專輯《[[愛荷華|愛荷華]]》風格黑暗，登上[[英國專輯排行榜|英國專輯排行榜]]第1名<ref name="books"/>，樂團更受歡迎<ref name="RS">{{cite web |language = en|last = Fricke |first = David |title = Iowa album review |work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石 (雜誌)]] |date = 2001-09-17 |url = http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/slipknot/albums/album/146645/review/5942405/iowa |accessdate = 2012-02-22 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071002075208/http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/slipknot/albums/album/146645/review/5942405/iowa |archivedate = 2007-10-02 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。2004年發行第三張專輯《{{link-en|第3輯：窺探潛意識|Vol. 3: (The Subliminal Verses)}}》，登上[[告示牌200大專輯榜|告示牌200大專輯榜]]第3名<ref name="books"/>。2006年憑〈{{link-en|Before I Forget|Before I Forget (song)}}〉獲[[第48屆葛萊美獎|第48屆葛萊美獎]]最佳金屬團體獎<ref name="Grammy">{{cite news |language = en |title = List of Grammy winners |publisher = CNN |date = 2006-02-09 |url = http://www.cnn.com/2006/SHOWBIZ/Music/02/09/grammys.list/index.html |accessdate = 2007-12-13 |archive-date = 2009-11-21 |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/5lSheSN0K?url=http://www.cnn.com/2006/SHOWBIZ/Music/02/09/grammys.list/index.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。2008年發行第四張專輯《{{link-en|絕望深淵|All Hope Is Gone}}》登上告示牌200大專輯榜第1名<ref name="SlipCharts">{{cite web |language=en |title=All Hope Is Gone is #1!! |publisher=Sparkart |date=2008-09-03 |url=http://slipknot1.silverback.sparkart.net/story/all/all_hope_is_gone_is_1-1 |accessdate=2008-09-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5aYydJpQI?url=http://slipknot1.silverback.sparkart.net/story/all/all_hope_is_gone_is_1-1 |archivedate=2008-09-03 }}</ref>後，又經過漫長沉寂，2014年才發行第五張專輯《{{link-en|灰五樂章|.5: The Gray Chapter}}》。他們被認為是[[美式重金屬新浪潮|美式重金屬新浪潮]]的龍頭樂團之一。經過漫長的沉寂，2019才再次發行第六張專輯《{{link-en|我們不是你這種人|We Are Not Your Kind}}》，在2019年8月登上[[告示牌二百大專輯榜|告示牌二百大專輯榜]]第一名<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title='New Wave Of American Heavy Metal' Book Documents Over 600 Bands |url=http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=44955 |publisher=Blabbermouth.net |accessdate=2008-04-27 |archive-date=2008-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080521104002/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=44955 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{link-de|Garry Sharpe-Young|Garry Sharpe-Young}}《Metal: The Definitive Guide》(2007)ISBN 978-1906002015</ref><ref name="zonda">{{cite web| language = en| url = http://www.zondabooks.com/titles/nwoahm/| publisher = Zondabooks| title = New Wave of American Heavy Metal| accessdate = 2006-05-06| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20060427093457/http://www.zondabooks.com/titles/nwoahm/| archivedate = 2006-04-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| language = en| url = http://www.metalexpressradio.com/menu.php?main=reviews&id=1013| publisher = Metal Express Radio| title = LAMB OF GOD - Burn The Priest| author = SHOEGAZER ROSS| accessdate = 2008-05-06| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090917140650/http://www.metalexpressradio.com/menu.php?main=reviews&id=1013| archive-date = 2009-09-17| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
=== 成立前的情況（1991 - 1995年） ===
Slipknot的形成歷史必須追溯至1991年，地點為美國愛荷華州的首府狄蒙。該區的金屬圈中，最大的樂團是「Atomic Opera」，其吉他手為{{link-en|Jim Root|Jim Root}}<ref name="McIver11">{{link-en|Joel McIver|Joel McIver}}《Slipknot Unmasked (Again)》(2003) ISBN 978-0711997646，第11頁</ref>。鼓手[[喬依·喬迪森|Joey Jordison]]成立了名為「Modifidious」的鞭擊金屬樂團，在一個名為"Runway"的俱樂部演奏。1991年12月1日，「Modifidious」在該俱樂部為「Atomic Opera」擔任暖場團。之後他的吉他手離團，由{{link-en|Craig Jones|Craig Jones (musician)}}接任<ref name="Arnopp31">Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第31–34頁</ref>。1992年7月，另一位鼓手{{link-en|Shawn Crahan|Shawn Crahan}}剛成立了名為「Heads on the Wall」的{{link-en|放克金屬|Funk metal}}翻唱樂團。

Slipknot後來的主唱Anders Colsefni則在一支死亡金屬樂團「Vexx」，他擔任鼓手，團裡的貝斯手是{{link-en|Paul Gray|Paul Gray (American musician)}}、吉他手則是Josh Brainard。後來，Colsefni接任主唱，但「Vexx」從未出過唱片。當時，Crahan經常在禮拜天去"Runway"，和那邊其他的年輕樂手一起玩即興演奏。1993年3月，Crahan與主唱Colsefni、貝斯手Gray和另一位樂手，在Gray住家的地下室一起創作音樂，並有了組團的想法。他們討論過團名取為「Pull My Finger」，但最終沒有實踐行動。當時，他們錄製了兩首名為〈Slipknot〉和〈Painface〉的曲子。多年後Colsefni用來命名他的樂團「{{link-en|Painface|Painface}}」<ref>Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第63頁</ref>。

1993年，當地成立一支名為「Inveigh Catharsis」的新樂團，貝斯手是Gray、吉他手是Brainard、鼓手是Colsefni，而Jordison偶爾會加入客串演奏。Brainard最後離開了「Inveigh Catharsis」、加入「Modifidious」。93年底和94年初他們完成了試聽帶。1994年，「Modifidious」有時會和Crahan的「Heads on the Wall」同台演出。這時Gray成立了名為「Body Pit」的死亡金屬樂團，這團快速的在當地受到歡迎<ref name="McIver11"/>。1995年初，「Modifidious」因興趣減退而解散。Gray邀請Jordison加入「Body Pit」，但失敗了。不久之後，他找來當地的吉他老師{{link-en|Mick Thomson|Mick Thomson}}加入<ref name="Arnopp31"/>。

=== 創建初期（1995 - 1998年） ===
1995年9月，Crahan和Gray一起成立了名為「Pale Ones」的新樂團，這是Slipknot的前身<ref name="Arnopp40">Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第40頁</ref>。其成員都是當地金屬圈中的樂手，其中包括主唱Colsefni和吉他手{{link-en|Donnie Steele|Donnie Steele}}<ref name="Arnopp40"/>。在他們展開新樂團不久，因為想實驗更多不一樣的鼓聲，Gray便邀請Jordison加入，排練後他立刻就表示想加入，成為了主要鼓手<ref name="Arnopp40"/>。此外，主唱Colsefni也同時負責打擊樂器的位置。他們後來又邀請Brainard加入成為第二吉他手。此時「Pale Ones」已有六名成員<ref name="Arnopp42">Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第42頁</ref>。同年12月4日，樂團首次公開演出，但對外公佈的團名叫做「Meld」<ref>Joel McIver《Slipknot Unmasked (Again)》(2003) ISBN 978-0711997646，第17頁</ref>。

1995年底的某天深夜，Gray和Crahan到Jordison上班的{{link-en|辛克來加油站|Sinclair Oil Corporation}}開會。當時，Jordison提出用〈Slipknot〉的曲名作為樂團的新名字。現在對Slipknot早期發展的回顧，經常將這次會議視為關鍵<ref name="Arnopp42"/>。12月，Slipknot開始在當地的SR Audio錄製音源<ref name="McIver19">Joel McIver《Slipknot Unmasked (Again)》(2003) ISBN 978-0711997646，第19頁</ref>。因缺乏4萬美金的錄音預算，成員自籌了這筆費用<ref name="Arnopp45">Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第45-47頁</ref>。1996年2月，吉他手Steele以信仰基督教為由離團。在混音後製的階段，Craig Jones被聘為替補吉他手<ref name="Arnopp50">Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第50-51頁</ref>。然而，在錄音室做出的音源卻無法在現場演出時弄出一樣的聲音。隨後，Jones也負責操作採樣器，Mick Thomson也被邀請加入擔任吉他手<ref name="Arnopp57">Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第57頁</ref>。

1996年10月31日，他們終於完成複雜的混音與母帶工程，製作了首張試聽帶《{{link-en|Mate. Feed. Kill. Repeat.|Mate. Feed. Kill. Repeat.}}》<ref name="AMG">{{cite news |language = en|last = Huey |first = Steve |title = Slipknot biography |publisher=Allmusic |url = {{Allmusic|class=artist|id=p41591|pure_url=yes}} |accessdate = 2007-12-13 }}</ref>。1997年夏天，獲得內布拉斯卡州一家名叫Ismist的小型唱片公司發行<ref name="McIver38-41">Joel McIver《Slipknot Unmasked (Again)》(2003) ISBN 978-0711997646，第38-41頁</ref>。Slipknot的作品在當地電台有少量的曝光，但並未吸引任何唱片公司的興趣，樂團便回到地下室繼續錄新的音源<ref name="McIver38-41"/>。這時樂團希望能在人聲上更加旋律化，於是公開招募，前來應徵的是「{{link-en|Stone Sour|Stone Sour}}」主唱{{link-en|Corey Taylor|Corey Taylor}}。他加入後擔任主唱，放棄了「Stone Sour」，而原主唱Colsefni則改為負責打擊樂器與和聲<ref name="Arnopp71">Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第71-74頁</ref>。樂團一邊錄音、一邊在當地進行演出。1997年9月，在其中一次演出時，舞台上的Colsefni宣布退團<ref name="Arnopp77">Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第77頁</ref>。打擊樂器的位置後來由Greg Welts遞補<ref>Joel McIver《Slipknot Unmasked (Again)》(2003) ISBN 978-0711997646，第47頁</ref>。

1998年初，為吸引唱片公司的注意，樂團又錄製了有五條音軌的試聽帶《Slipknot》<ref name="Arnopp83">Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第83頁</ref>，這才開始受到多間唱片公司的關注。1998年2月，音樂製作人{{link-en|Ross Robinson|Ross Robinson}}來到狄蒙為他們排練、製作首張專輯<ref name="Arnopp84">Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第84-89頁</ref>。不久之後，前來應徵DJ位置的{{link-en|Sid Wilson|Sid Wilson}}，引起樂團極大的興趣。自此，以Crahan為首的這支樂團，最終形成多達九人的固定陣容，他們分別以0到8的九個數字來代表每名成員。成立之初就以面具作為最重要的表演工具，無論到哪裡都只見面具，而不見他們的廬山真面目<ref name="Arnopp91">Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第91頁</ref>。1998年6月底，得到一家較大的公司{{link-en|Roadrunner唱片|Roadrunner Records}}欣賞。7月16日，Welts被樂團開除，原因並未公開<ref name="McIver54"/>。7月18日，Slipknot和Roadrunner唱片公司正式簽約，獲得一紙50萬美金、七張專輯的合約<ref name="McIver54">Joel McIver《Slipknot Unmasked (Again)》(2003) ISBN 978-0711997646，第54頁</ref>。之後，由{{link-en|Brandon Darner|Brandon Darner}}遞補打擊樂器手。

=== 首張同名專輯及突破（1998 - 2000年） ===
1998年9月，在樂團前往加州馬里布市錄製首張專輯前，{{link-en|Chris Fehn|Chris Fehn}}取代了Darner成為打擊樂器手<ref>Joel McIver《Slipknot Unmasked (Again)》(2003) ISBN 978-0711997646，第57-58頁</ref>。在聖誕節期間，樂團回到家鄉狄蒙錄製一部分音源，吉他手Brainard決定離團<ref>Mark Crampton《Barcode Killers: The Slipknot Story in Words and Pictures》(2002) ISBN 978-1842401262，第35頁</ref>。Brainard說：「我不怎麼滿意樂團的一些決策」<ref name="Root">Joel McIver《Slipknot Unmasked (Again)》(2003) ISBN 978-0711997646，第61-63頁</ref>。Slipknot隨後招募了Jim Root成為正式吉他手，並回到馬里布市繼續專輯錄製<ref name="Root"/>。1999年初，錄製工作結束。6月29日發行了第一張正式的專輯《Slipknot》<ref name="AMG1Album">{{cite news |language = en|last = Anderson |first = Rick |title = Slipknot album review |publisher=Allmusic |url = {{Allmusic|class=album|id=r183561|pure_url=yes}} |accessdate = 2007-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111024021802/http://www.allmusic.com/album/r183561|archive-date=2011-10-24}}</ref>。年中，樂團不停的巡演，並首度參加[[Ozzy_Osbourne|Ozzy Osbourne]]創建的{{link-en|Ozzfest|Ozzfest}}音樂節<ref name="AMG"/>。有多位成員在表演時發洩過度而受傷，Crahan的頭部甚至需要縫針，不過鮮血換來更廣泛的人氣。暴力、甚至有些血腥的演出，透過電視轉播而征服了眾多金屬迷，極大提高了知名度。在Ozzfest演出後，樂團擁有了自己的固定歌迷群。他們的單曲〈{{link-en|Wait and Bleed|Wait and Bleed}}〉和〈{{link-en|Spit It Out|Spit It Out (Slipknot song)}}〉馬上受到市場的歡迎。樂團透過巡演和口碑迅速獲得人氣<ref name="AMG"/>，1999年至2000年為宣傳出道專輯，到許多國家進行了巡迴演出。專輯登上告示牌200大專輯榜前50名，並且在全美範圍內突破一百萬張銷量，最終獲得[[美國唱片業協會|美國唱片業協會]]頒發2×白金唱片認證<ref name="RIAA.com"/>，這在Roadrunner唱片公司的歷史上還是第一次<ref name="XP">{{cite video |language = en|date = 2001 |title = Slipknot – X-Posed, The Interview |medium = CD |time = 7:00 |location = UK |publisher=Chrome Dreams}}</ref>。

=== 專輯《愛荷華》、沉寂（2001 - 2003年） ===
2001年，Slipknot已經成為美國最受關注的重金屬樂團之一。年初，樂團在洛杉磯的{{link-en|Sound City|Sound City Studios}}和Sound Image studios開始錄製第二張專輯<ref name="AMG"/><ref>Dick Porter《Rapcore: The Nu-Metal Rap Fusion》(2003) ISBN 978-0859653213，第132頁</ref>。由於大量的巡演和錄音計劃，成員之間產生了衝突<ref name="drum!">{{cite news |language = en|title = Joey Jordison plunges into Slipknot hell |work=Drum! |pages = 第44–45頁 |date =2008-10}}</ref>。2001年2月，結束錄製工作。5月起，樂團展開了{{link-en|愛荷華世界巡迴演唱會|Iowa World Tour}}<ref>{{cite news |language = en|title=Rebels with a Cause |work=[[Daily_Record|Daily Record]] |date=2002-01-25 |author=Cartiona Killin|page=第62頁 }}</ref>。8月28日，發行第二張專輯《愛荷華》，雖然面臨眾多專輯的競爭，但仍登上告示牌200大專輯榜第3名以及英國專輯排行榜第1名<ref name="Billboard">{{cite magazine |language = en |url = http://www.billboard.com/artist/279598/slipknot/chart |title = Billboard.com's page on Iowa |accessdate = 2010-09-12 |magazine = Billboard |archive-date = 2013-02-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130216055601/http://www.billboard.com/artist/279598/slipknot/chart |dead-url = no }}</ref>，全美銷量超過88萬張。該專輯製作了三首單曲〈{{link-en|The Heretic Anthem|The Heretic Anthem}}〉、〈[[末日迷蹤|Left Behind]]〉與〈{{link-en|My Plague|My Plague}}〉，成為電影《[[惡靈古堡_(電影)|惡靈古堡]]》的主題曲<ref name="NME666">{{cite news |language = en |title = The joy of 666 |work = NME |location = UK |date = 2001-05-15 |url = http://www.nme.com/news/slipknot/7781 |accessdate = 2009-04-25 |archive-date = 2012-10-11 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121011204327/http://www.nme.com/news/slipknot/7781 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120804/soundtrack |title=Resident Evil (2002) – Soundtracks |publisher=[[網路電影資料庫|網路電影資料庫]] |accessdate=2008-09-05 |archive-date=2009-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090215064345/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120804/soundtrack |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2002年，樂團在電影《{{link-en|極速風暴|Rollerball (2002 film)}}》中客串演出，並演唱了一曲〈I Am Hated〉<ref>{{cite news |title = Archive News |publisher = {{link-en|Blabbermouth.net|Blabbermouth.net}} |date = 2001-08-06 |url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=186 |accessdate = 2010-09-11 |archive-date = 2004-01-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20040128181810/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=186 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。經由這次的專輯發行和宣傳，樂團在幾個國家大型演出的門票都熱銷完售<ref>Joel McIver《Slipknot Unmasked (Again)》(2003) ISBN 978-0711997646，第103頁</ref>。

2002年中，樂團在巡演結束之後成立了自己的Maggot Recordings唱片公司，並簽下一支名為「Downthesun」的樂團，主唱是Crahan的調鼓師。經歷了瘋狂的巡迴演出後，樂團因內部衝突開始走向分裂。幾位成員開始各自分頭活動，樂團也面臨第一次沉寂<ref name="McIver107">Joel McIver《Slipknot Unmasked (Again)》(2003) ISBN 978-0711997646，第107-110頁}</ref>。主唱Taylor和吉他手Root重組了「Stone Sour」、鼓手Jordison成立「{{link-en|Murderdolls|Murderdolls}}」、打擊樂手Crahan成立「{{link-en|To My Surprise|To My Surprise}}」、Mick Thompson開始個人音樂發展、DJ Wilson更名為DJ Starscream開始個人發展、鼓手Jordison則加入「the Rejects」<ref name="McIver107"/>。Slipknot的分裂不斷加劇中，有一段時間像是活動休止般，無法確定他們何時才會重聚。關於是否會有第三張專輯、是否將會永久解散都成為各界猜測的話題<ref>{{cite video |language = en|people = Charlotte Lewin (Director) |title = Slipknot – Up To Our Necks |time = 57:51 |medium = DVD |publisher=Chrome Dreams |location = UK |date = 2004}}</ref>。

2002年底，主唱Taylor在樂團官網上發表聲明，他表示成員間已經幾個月沒講話了，樂團寧願解散也不要成為下一個「{{link-en|Gwar|Gwar}}」。這篇聲明引起「Gwar」的主唱{{link-en|Oderous Urungus|Dave Brockie}}與Taylor在網路上互相叫罵，不過這篇聲明也重新凝聚Slipknot的成員。2003年初，官網上Taylor的聲明被刪除，取而代之的是樂團宣布成員重聚，並且著手開始新專輯的錄製工作。

=== 專輯《第3輯：窺探潛意識》、二度沉寂（2003 - 2007年） ===
[[File:Slipknot_at_Bex_Rock_2005_12.jpg|180px]]
幾經耽擱，2003年中，Slipknot搬進洛杉磯的{{link-en|The Mansion|The Mansion (recording studio)}}錄音室、與大牌製作人{{link-en|Rick Rubin|Rick Rubin}}展開睽違三年的新專輯錄製<ref>{{cite news |language = en |title = Slipknot Singer Says 'A Lot Has Changed' With The Band Since 'Iowa' |publisher = Blabbermouth.net |date = 2003-08-05 |url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=14180 |accessdate = 2010-09-11 |archive-date = 2003-10-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20031013230339/http://roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=14180 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。2004年初，錄製工作結束後，再次展開{{link-en|The Subliminal Verses世界巡迴|The Subliminal Verses World Tour}}、{{link-en|Jägermeister音樂巡迴|Jägermeister Music Tour}}<ref>{{cite news|language = en|accessdate=2008-07-15|url=http://www.vh1.com/news/articles/1485648/20040309/slipknot.jhtml|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080426020545/http://www.vh1.com/news/articles/1485648/20040309/slipknot.jhtml|archivedate=2008-04-26|title=Slipknot Ready To Unveil New Masks, Subliminal LP|publisher=[[VH1|VH1]]|date=2004-09-03|author=Jon Wiederhorn}}</ref>與Ozzfest音樂節的演出，並配戴新設計的第三代面具。2004年5月25日，發行第三張專輯《第3輯：窺探潛意識》，登上告示牌200大專輯榜第2名<ref name="Road Runner">{{cite news |language = en|url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/artists/Slipknot/bio.aspx |title = Band Bio on Roadrunnerrecords.com |accessdate = 2007-02-11 |publisher=Roadrunner Records |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070126125334/http://roadrunnerrecords.com/artists/Slipknot/bio.aspx |archivedate = 2007-01-26}}</ref>。這張專輯製作了6支單曲：〈{{link-en|Duality|Duality (song)}}〉、〈{{link-en|Vermilion|Vermilion (song)}}〉、〈{{link-en|Vermilion, Pt. 2|Vermilion (song)#Vermilion Pt. 2}}〉、〈{{link-en|Before I Forget|Before I Forget (song)}}〉、〈{{link-en|The Nameless|The Nameless}}〉以及〈{{link-en|The Blister Exists|The Blister Exists}}〉。巡演期間，樂團也錄製了第一張現場專輯《{{link-en|9.0: Live|9.0: Live}}》，在2005年11月1日發行，它登上告示牌200大專輯榜第17名<ref name="BillboardLive">{{cite magazine |language = en |url = http://www.billboard.com/artist/279598/slipknot/chart |title = Billboard.com's listing of 9.0:Live |accessdate = 2010-09-12 |magazine = Billboard |archive-date = 2013-02-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130216055601/http://www.billboard.com/artist/279598/slipknot/chart |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2005年，幾名成員參與了唱片公司的25週年合輯《{{link-en|Roadrunner United|Roadrunner United}}》。2006年，樂團贏得第一座[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]：以〈Before I Forget〉獲第48屆{{link-en|最佳金屬樂演奏|Grammy Award for Best Metal Performance}}獎<ref name="Grammy"/>。2006年12月5日，發行第三張影像作品《{{link-en|Voliminal: Inside the Nine|Voliminal: Inside the Nine}}》<ref name="VoliminalArt">{{cite news |language = en |url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=60348 |title = Slipknot: new DVD artwork revealed |date = 2006-10-16 |accessdate = 2006-10-16 |publisher = Blabbermouth.net |archive-date = 2008-06-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080617093407/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=60348 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。之後，樂團進入第二次沉寂，每個成員都放了長假：主唱Taylor和吉他手Root回到「Stone Sour」、鼓手Jordison參與「{{link-en|3 Inches of Blood|3 Inches of Blood}}」的專輯製作、打擊樂手Crahan成立「{{link-en|Dirty Little Rabbits|Dirty Little Rabbits}}」，DJ Wilson又回到DJ Starscream的個人名義活動。

=== 專輯《絕望深淵》、三度沉寂、創團貝斯手驟逝（2008 - 2010年） ===
[[File:Metaltown_2009,_Slipknot.jpg|180px]]
2007年底，樂團成員在{{link-en|Sound Farm錄音室|Sound Farm Studio & Recording Environment}}集結，與製作人{{link-en|Dave Fortman|Dave Fortman}}合作，展開新專輯錄製<ref name="JoeyBrutal">{{cite magazine|language = en|title=Slipknot man promises brutal new album in '08 |url=http://www2.kerrang.com/2007/07/slipknot_man_promises_brutal_n.html |date=2007-07-20 |accessdate=2007-11-29 |magazine={{link-en|Kerrang!|Kerrang!}} |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071108234029/http://www2.kerrang.com/2007/07/slipknot_man_promises_brutal_n.html |archivedate=2007-11-08 }}</ref><ref name="RevAugust">{{cite magazine |language = en|last = Epstein |first = Dan |date=2008-08 |title = Wait and Bleed |magazine=[[Revolver|Revolver]] |pages = 第54-56頁 }}</ref>。2008年1月結束錄音，預計2月發行，但樂團聽了混音後不滿意，於是又回到錄音室重做，直到6月才完工。7月9日，展開{{link-en|絕望深淵世界巡迴演唱會|All Hope Is Gone World Tour}}<ref>{{cite news |language = en |title = Slipknot, Disturbed, Dragonforce, Mastodon: Complete 'Rockstar Energy Mayhem' Details Revealed |publisher = Blabbermouth.net |date = 2008-01-30 |url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=89637 |accessdate = 2010-09-11 |archive-date = 2008-04-22 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080422012018/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=89637 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。8月20日，發行第四張專輯《絕望深淵》，首次登上告示牌200大專輯榜第1名<ref>{{cite magazine |language = en |url = http://www.billboard.com/artist/279598/slipknot/chart |title = Billboard.com's page on All Hope Is Gone |accessdate = 2010-09-12 |magazine = Billboard |archive-date = 2013-02-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130216055601/http://www.billboard.com/artist/279598/slipknot/chart |dead-url = no }}</ref>。與上張專輯偏重鞭擊金屬的風格不同，這次出現大量吉他獨奏、木吉他，以及旋律優美的演唱。對於死忠的資深樂迷來說，《絕望深淵》或許已經沒有他們所期待的東西，如今的Slipknot似乎正在向Taylor的分支樂團「Stone Sour」方向發展<ref>{{cite book|language= en|title= New Wave of American Heavy Metal|last= Sharpe-Young|first= Garry|year= |publisher= Zonda Books Limited|url= http://books.google.com/books?id=uIIf03bGyAAC&pg=PP10&dq=nwoahm&ei=a7ohSNGYCrW2iQGP95nFDQ&sig=yhEpvA_dhNF6I5YwMJACJGRA3XY#PPP10,M1|isbn= 0958268401|pages= ix|access-date= 2008-07-29|archive-date= 2015-03-22|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150322154044/http://books.google.com/books?id=uIIf03bGyAAC&pg=PP10&dq=nwoahm&ei=a7ohSNGYCrW2iQGP95nFDQ&sig=yhEpvA_dhNF6I5YwMJACJGRA3XY#PPP10,M1|dead-url= no}}</ref>。這張專輯製作了5支單曲：〈{{link-en|All Hope Is Gone|All Hope Is Gone (song)}}〉、〈{{link-en|Psychosocial|Psychosocial (song)}}〉、〈{{link-en|Dead Memories|Dead Memories (song)}}〉、〈[[Sulfur|Sulfur]]〉以及〈{{link-en|Snuff|Snuff (song)}}〉。

2009年9月9日，為紀念樂團出道十週年，發行《Slipknot》的特別版<ref>{{Cite news|language = en|title=Slipknot to Release Special 10th Anniversary Debut |publisher=Roadrunner Records |date=2009-07-27 |url=http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/news/Slipknot-to-Release-Special-10th-Anniversary-Debut-20413.aspx |accessdate=2010-09-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090731113002/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/news/Slipknot-to-Release-Special-10th-Anniversary-Debut-20413.aspx |archivedate=2009-07-31 }}</ref>。2008年一直到2009年10月31日，樂團都在進行新專輯的巡迴演出。之後，進入第三次的沉寂<ref name="DefShows">{{cite news |language = en |title = Slipknot Announces Fall Tour Dates |publisher = Blabbermouth.net |date = 2009-09-03 |url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=126417 |accessdate = 2009-09-03 |archive-date = 2009-09-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090907010905/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=126417 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。成員再度分頭活動，主唱Taylor與吉他手Root回到「Stone Sour」並成立「{{link-en|Junk Beer Kidnap Band|Junk Beer Kidnap Band}}」、打擊樂手Crahan繼續「Dirty Little Rabbits」的活動、鼓手Jordison回到「Murderdolls」並成為[[Rob_Zombie|Rob Zombie]]新的正式鼓手、打擊樂手Fehn加入金屬核樂團「{{link-en|Will Haven|Will Haven}}」，DJ Wilson則成立了新團「Sid」。
{{Quote box|width=25em|align=left|quote=“我唯一能夠形容Paul的詞彙就是──愛”|source=<small>主唱Corey Taylor在Paul Gray的逝世記者會表示</small><ref>{{cite news |language = en |title = Slipknot Holds News Conference To Address Passing Of Bassist Paul Gray |publisher = Blabbermouth.net |date = 2010-05-25 |url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=140671 |accessdate = 2010-09-11 |archive-date = 2010-07-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100726092602/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=140671 |dead-url = no }}</ref>}}
2010年，Gray計畫加入[[超級樂團|超級樂團]]「{{link-en|Hail!|Hail!}}」並一起巡演。然而，5月24日早上，警方在愛荷華州的旅館裡發現Gray的屍體<ref>{{cite news|language= en|url= http://www.fmqb.com/article.asp?id=1816394|title= Slipknot Bassist Paul Gray Found Dead|publisher= {{link-en|FMQB|FMQB}}|date= 2010-05-24|accessdate= 2010-08-20|deadurl= yes|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20170322024723/http://www.fmqb.com/article.asp?id=1816394|archivedate= 2017-03-22}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |language = en |title = Slipknot bassist Paul Gray dead |publisher = {{link-en|地鐵報|Metro (British newspaper)}} |date = 2010-05-25 |url = http://www.metro.co.uk/music/827689-slipknot-bassist-paul-gray-dead |accessdate = 2010-09-11 |archive-date = 2010-05-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100529165923/http://www.metro.co.uk/music/827689-slipknot-bassist-paul-gray-dead |dead-url = no }}</ref>，當時死因並未明朗，[[驗屍|驗屍]]後懷疑他的死並非自殺，但官方沒有透露原因<ref>{{cite news|language= en|url= http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2010-05-25-slipknot-bassist-autopsy_N.htm|title= Autopsy fails to determine cause of death of Slipknot bassist|work= [[今日美國|今日美國]]|date= 2010-05-25|accessdate= 2010-08-20|archive-date= 2010-05-28|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100528172701/http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2010-05-25-slipknot-bassist-autopsy_N.htm|dead-url= no}}</ref>。他去世後的第二天，樂團其餘八名成員取消了公演，全體陪同Gray的遺孀和弟弟舉行記者會<ref>{{cite news|language = en|url=http://www.slipknot1.com/story/news/slipknot_holding_live_press_conference |title=Slipknot Holding Live Press Conference |publisher=slipknot1.com |date=2010-05-25 |accessdate=2010-08-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100528081834/http://www.slipknot1.com/story/news/slipknot_holding_live_press_conference |archivedate=2010-05-28 }}</ref>。6月21日，調查報告確認Paul Gray是死於注射過量的[[嗎啡|嗎啡]]和[[芬太尼|吩坦尼]]<ref>{{cite news|language=en|last=Goldsmith|first=Belinda|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/957674/slipknot-bassist-died-of-accidental-overdose|title=Slipknot Bassist Died Of 'Accidental' Overdose|agency=Reuters|date=2010-06-22|accessdate=2010-08-20|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309041856/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/957674/slipknot-bassist-died-of-accidental-overdose|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Gray逝世後，成員對Slipknot的未來猶豫不決，他們在各自的採訪中看法不一。鼓手Jordison向「The Pulse Of Radio」透露已經在醞釀Slipknot的新專輯<ref>{{cite news |language = en |title = Slipknot Drummer: Paul Gray 'Would Always Want Us To Make Another Record' |publisher = Blabbermouth.net |date = 2010-08-03 |url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=143938 |accessdate = 2010-09-11 |archive-date = 2011-09-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110921193358/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=143938 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。主唱Taylor向「{{link-en|FMQB|FMQB}}」表示，他非常掙扎還要不要繼續Slipknot的活動<ref>{{cite news |language = en |title = Corey Taylor 'Conflicted' About Continuing Slipknot |publisher = Blabbermouth.net |date = 2010-09-05 |url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=145556 |accessdate = 2010-09-11 |archive-date = 2011-09-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110921032123/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=145556 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。9月28日，樂團發行第四個影像作品《{{link-en|(sic)nesses|(sic)nesses}}》<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url=http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/news/Slipknots-sicnesses-is-Out-Now-Get-Another-Exclusive-Look-at-the-DVD-From-Kerrang-22164.aspx |title=SLIPKNOT'S '(SIC)NESSES' IS OUT NOW, GET ANOTHER EXCLUSIVE LOOK AT THE DVD FROM 'KERRANG!' |publisher=Roadrunner |date=2010-09-28 |accessdate=2010-10-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101012185019/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/news/Slipknots-sicnesses-is-Out-Now-Get-Another-Exclusive-Look-at-the-DVD-From-Kerrang-22164.aspx |archivedate=2010-10-12 }}</ref>，它在[[告示牌榜單|告示牌榜單]]、{{link-en|英國影片排行榜|UK Video Charts}}、[[澳大利亞唱片業協會榜|澳洲唱片榜]]及{{link-en|芬蘭官方排行榜|The Official Finnish Charts}}都登上第1名<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=147272|title = SLIPKNOT's '(Sic)nesses' DVD Tops 'Music Videos' Chart - Oct. 6, 2010|publisher = Blabbermouth|date = 2010-10-06|accessdate = 2010-10-11|archive-date = 2012-06-29|archive-url = https://archive.today/20120629134217/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=147272|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=146561|title = Slipknot: '(sic)nesses' DVD Clown's Director's Cut Screenings Announced|publisher = Blabbermouth.net|date = 2010-09-23|accessdate = 2010-09-23}}</ref>。這支影片完整收錄了2009年樂團在{{link-en|Download音樂節|Download Festival}}的演出、45分鐘的巡演幕後紀錄片，以及四個音樂錄影帶<ref>{{cite news|language= en|url= http://roadrunnerrecords.co.uk/page/News?news_id=99244|title= Slipknot to release '(sic)nesses' DVD- September 28th|publisher= Roadrunner Records|date= 2010-08-19|accessdate= 2010-08-19|archive-date= 2019-05-28|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190528225051/http://roadrunnerrecords.co.uk/page/News/?news_id=99244|dead-url= no}}</ref>，並悼念逝去的Paul Gray<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1648519/20100923/slipknot.jhtml|title = Slipknot Dedicate '(Sic)nesses' DVD To Paul Gray|last = Montgomery|first = James|date = 2010-09-23|accessdate = 2010-10-11|archive-date = 2010-12-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101230165053/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1648519/20100923/slipknot.jhtml|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 重返舞台，精選輯《終極地獄》、創建Knotfest（2010 - 2012年） ===
[[File:Slipknot_@_Claremont_Showgrounds_(5_3_2012)_(6859500036).jpg|180px]]
關於樂團的未來，主唱Taylor告訴《[[新音樂快遞|新音樂快遞]]》，Gray期望他們能續繼維持下去，但他心中仍存有矛盾<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.nme.com/news/slipknot/54138|title = Corey Taylor: 'Paul Gray would want Slipknot to continue' - video|work = [[新音樂快遞|新音樂快遞]]|location = UK|date = 2010-12-06|accessdate = 2010-12-06|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304052248/http://www.nme.com/news/slipknot/54138|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2011年，樂團重返舞台，在歐洲進行少量的演出。他們參加了{{link-en|Sonisphere Festival|Sonisphere Festival}}與{{link-en|Rock in Rio|Rock in Rio}}，和[[Iron_Maiden|Iron Maiden]]、[[Metallica|Metallica]]同台演出<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url=http://www.slipknot1.com/story/news-tour_news/slipknot_return_in_2011-1 |title=Slipknot return 2011 |publisher=Slipknot1.com |date=2010-12-03 |accessdate=2010-12-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101206065421/http://www.slipknot1.com/story/news-tour_news/slipknot_return_in_2011-1 |archivedate=2010-12-06 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|language = en|url=http://www.slipknot1.com/story/news-outside_the_9-ot9_news/slipknot_to_headline_graspop |title=Slipknot to headline graspop |publisher=slipknot1.com |date=2010-12-05 |accessdate=2010-12-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101210013527/http://slipknot1.com/story/news-outside_the_9-ot9_news/slipknot_to_headline_graspop |archivedate=2010-12-10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|language = en|url=http://www.slipknot1.com/story/news/slipknot_confirmed_for_rock_in_rio |title=Slipknot confirmed for rock in rio |publisher=slipknot1.com |date=2010-12-08 |accessdate=2010-12-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101211103336/http://www.slipknot1.com/story/news/slipknot_confirmed_for_rock_in_rio |archivedate=2010-12-11 }}</ref>。已離開多年的創團成員Donnie Steele，回到樂團中支援貝斯的現場演奏，他站的位置隱藏在鼓手Jordison後面，以至於觀眾看不到他<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url=http://slipknot1.com/story/news/update_regarding_summer_shows-1 |title=Update regarding summer shows |publisher=slipknot1.com |date=2011-03-10 |accessdate=2011-03-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110313012708/http://slipknot1.com/story/news/update_regarding_summer_shows-1 |archivedate=2011-03-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=159643|title = SLIPKNOT's First Show Since Death Of PAUL GRAY: HD Video Footage Available - 2011-06-20|publisher = Blabbermouth.net|date = 2011-06-21|accessdate = 2011-09-03|archive-date = 2011-08-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110821043327/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=159643|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

Slipknot表示，樂團將完成並發行第五張錄音室專輯，而且還不打算找人遞補Gray的位置<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=154920|title = COREY TAYLOR On Possibility Of Another SLIPKNOT Album: 'I Don't See It Happening Very Soon'|date = 2011-03-04|accessdate = 2011-03-05|archive-date = 2011-03-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110308230932/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=154920|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/950116/slipknot-prepping-first-album-since-bassists-death|title = Slipknot Prepping First Album Since Bassist's Death|last = Graff|first = Gary|date = 2010-11-30|accessdate = 2010-12-10|archive-date = 2021-03-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308091103/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/950116/slipknot-prepping-first-album-since-bassists-death|dead-url = no}}</ref>。鼓手Jordison表示，這張專輯已經開始創作，他寫了17首歌曲。之後，樂團參加了{{link-en|Mayhem音樂節2012|Mayhem Festival 2012}}的演出<ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite web|language = en|url=http://rockstarmayhemfest.com/blog/id/1845118 |title=Rockstar Mayhem Festival/Blog/2012 Dates Announced |publisher=Rockstarmayhemfest.com |accessdate=2011-10-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111104152448/http://rockstarmayhemfest.com/blog/id/1845118 |archivedate=2011-11-04 }}</ref>。

2012年5月29日，Roadrunner唱片公司在其官方網站上發布精選輯《{{link-en|終極地獄|Antennas to Hell}}》的預告片<ref name="greatest hits and demos">{{cite web|language=en|url=http://loudwire.com/slipknot-prepping-greatest-hits-release-working-on-new-demos/|title=Slipknot Prepping Greatest Hits Release, Working on New Demos|publisher={{link-en|Loudwire|Loudwire}}|first=Chad|last=Boward|date=2012-05-29|accessdate=2012-05-30|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224040402/https://loudwire.com/slipknot-prepping-greatest-hits-release-working-on-new-demos/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當天稍晚，主唱Taylor在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上說：「樂團尚未展開正式錄製，但已做出試聽帶了」<ref name="greatest hits and demos"/>。

2012年中，Slipknot創建了名為「{{link-en|Knotfest|Knotfest}}」的金屬音樂節，8月17日在愛荷華州的[[康瑟尔布拉夫斯_(艾奥瓦州)|康瑟爾崖]]舉辦，8月18日在威斯康辛州的小鎮[[薩默塞特|薩默塞特]]舉辦，[[Deftones|Deftones]]、[[Lamb_of_God|Lamb of God]]、{{link-en|Cannibal Corpse|Cannibal Corpse}}與{{link-en|Machine Head|Machine Head}}等樂團都參與了演出活動。同時場內還展示了Slipknot博物館<ref name="RSknotfest">{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/exclusive-slipknot-unveil-knotfest-20120604|title=Slipknot to launch own music festival, Knotfest|publisher=滾石雜誌|first=Steve|last=Baltin|date=2012-06-04|accessdate=2012-06-04|archive-date=2017-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912024701/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/exclusive-slipknot-unveil-knotfest-20120604|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年6月14日，樂團二度參加Download音樂節，演出時聚集約9萬人，並有兩次舞台前方的護欄被爆滿的觀眾擠壞、因維修而暫停演出<ref name="DownloadBBC">{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/22917617|title=Slipknot close first night of Download rock festival|publisher=[[英國廣播公司新聞頻道|英國廣播公司新聞頻道]]|date=2013-06-15|accessdate=2013-06-20|archive-date=2014-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140207224730/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/22917617|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 創團鼓手離團、專輯《灰五樂章》及新成員加入（2013年至2016年） ===
[[File:Slipknot_at_Roskilde_Festival_2013.jpg|180px]]
2013年底，樂團開始著手錄製新專輯，Taylor描述它將會是「非常黑暗的」一張專輯，風格介於《愛荷華》與《第3輯：窺探潛意識》<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.metalinjection.net/latest-news/slipknot-frontman-says-new-demos-are-really-dark-will-be-a-mix-of-iowa-vol-4|title = SLIPKNOT Frontman Says New Material Is "Really Dark," Will Be A Mix of Iowa & Vol. 3|publisher = ''MetalInjection ''|first = Greg|last = Kennelty|date = 2013-10-21|accessdate = 2013-12-07|archive-date = 2019-06-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190610134318/https://metalinjection.net/latest-news/slipknot-frontman-says-new-demos-are-really-dark-will-be-a-mix-of-iowa-vol-4|dead-url = no}}</ref>。吉他手Root為專心創作Slipknot的音樂，離開了「Stone Sour」<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.metalinjection.net/upcoming-releases/slipknot-so-serious-about-writing-new-music-that-guitarist-jim-root-is-sitting-out-the-next-stone-sour-tour|title = SLIPKNOT So Serious About Writing New Music That Guitarist Jim Root Is Sitting Out The Next STONE SOUR Tour|publisher = MetalInjection|first = Robert|last = Pasbani|date = 2013-12-04|accessdate = 2013-12-07|archive-date = 2021-02-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225040542/https://metalinjection.net/upcoming-releases/slipknot-so-serious-about-writing-new-music-that-guitarist-jim-root-is-sitting-out-the-next-stone-sour-tour|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2013年12月12日，樂團官網公布已待了18年的創團鼓手Joey Jordison離開的消息，理由是個人原因<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5839723/slipknot-drummer-joey-jordison-part-ways|title = Slipknot, Drummer Joey Jordison Part Ways|publisher = ''Billboard''|first = Kevin|last = Rutherford|date = 2013-12-13|accessdate = 2013-12-14|archive-date = 2014-09-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140919144905/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5839723/slipknot-drummer-joey-jordison-part-ways|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/dec/13/drummer-joey-jordisonleaves-slipknot |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6guLCxaDl?url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/dec/13/drummer-joey-jordison-leaves-slipknot |archivedate=2016-04-20 |title=Slipknot drummer Joey Jordison leaves band |publisher=''The Guardian'' |date=2013-12-13 |accessdate=2013-12-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.nme.com/news/slipknot/74397|title = Drummer Joey Jordison leaves Slipknot|publisher = NME|date = 2013-12-13|accessdate = 2013-12-14|archive-date = 2014-10-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141009221527/http://www.nme.com/news/slipknot/74397|dead-url = no}}</ref>。在Jordison的個人[[Facebook|Facebook]]專頁上，他表示「我想的非常清楚，我沒有放棄Slipknot。這支樂團在過去18年裡一直是我的人生，我永遠不會拋棄它，包括我的樂迷」<ref name="Jordison">{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.metalinjection.net/latest-news/drama/joey-jordison-i-did-not-quit-slipknot|title = Joey Jordison: "I Did Not Quit SLIPKNOT"|publisher = {{link-en|Metal Injection|Metal Injection}}|first = Greg|last = Kennelty|date = 2014-01-02|accessdate = 2014-01-09|archive-date = 2015-11-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151107013635/http://www.metalinjection.net/latest-news/drama/joey-jordison-i-did-not-quit-slipknot|dead-url = no}}</ref>。主唱Taylor透露，新專輯中沒有Jordison的鼓聲與創作，因為他離團前沒有參與任何詞曲創作的會議<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://loudwire.com/corey-taylor-first-interview-joey-jordison-departure-slipknot/|title = Corey taylor gives first interview following joey jordison's departure from slipknot|publisher = Loudwire|first = Graham|last = Hartmann|date = 2013-12-13|accessdate = 2013-12-14|archive-date = 2016-02-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160222113736/http://loudwire.com/corey-taylor-first-interview-joey-jordison-departure-slipknot/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。直到2016年6月，Jordison才透露當時已罹患橫斷性脊髓炎，雙腿感覺是被切斷的<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://teamrock.com/news/2016-06-16/joey-jordison-carried-onstage-for-final-slipknot-shows|title = Joey Jordison had to be carried onstage for his final Slipknot shows|publisher = TeamRock|author = Scott Munro|date = 2016-06-16|accessdate = 2016-09-16|archive-date = 2018-03-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180322174352/http://teamrock.com/news/2016-06-16/joey-jordison-carried-onstage-for-final-slipknot-shows|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2014年7月，Slipknot在樂團官網和社交媒體上，開始用神秘訊息和血腥圖片透露關於新專輯的消息<ref name="Album 5 Teasers">{{cite web|language=en|last1=Childers|first1=Chad|title=Slipknot reveal fifth new album teaser trailer|url=http://loudwire.com/slipknot-fifth-teaser/|website=Loudwire.com|publisher=Loudwire|accessdate=2014-08-03|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227073414/https://loudwire.com/slipknot-fifth-teaser/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Album 5 cryptic messages">{{cite web|language=en|last1=Hartmann|first1=Graham|title=Slipknot Continue to Tease New Album With Cryptic Written Message|url=http://loudwire.com/slipknot-continue-tease-new-album-cryptic-text-message/|website=Loudwire.com|publisher=Loudwire|accessdate=2014-08-03|archive-date=2021-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312002922/https://loudwire.com/slipknot-continue-tease-new-album-cryptic-text-message/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月1日，作為給樂迷的禮物，在新專輯完成前、發表了睽違6年的第一首新曲〈{{link-en|The Negative One|The Negative One}}〉<ref name="The Negative One release">{{cite web|language=en|last1=Grow|first1=Kory|title=Slipknot Stream 'The Negative One,' Their First New Song in Six Years|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/slipknot-stream-the-negative-one-their-first-new-song-in-six-years-20140801|website=Rollingstone.com|publisher=RollingStone|accessdate=2014-08-03|archive-date=2017-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171211213703/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/slipknot-stream-the-negative-one-their-first-new-song-in-six-years-20140801|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月5日，該曲的音樂錄影帶在樂團的[[YouTube|YouTube]]頻道上傳，影片中成員都沒有入鏡<ref name="The Negative One music video">{{cite web|language=en|last1=Grow|first1=Kory|title=See Slipknot's Nightmarish, NSFW 'Negative One' Video|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/videos/see-slipknots-nightmarish-nsfw-negative-one-video-20140805|website=Rollingstone.com|publisher=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2014-08-07|archive-date=2018-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180105123117/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/videos/see-slipknots-nightmarish-nsfw-negative-one-video-20140805|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月24日，在電台和音樂頻道上發表了新曲〈{{link-en|The Devil in I|The Devil in I}}〉，並預告了新專輯的命名和發行日期<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/slipknot-to-film-video-for-new-single-the-devil-in-i/|title = SLIPKNOT To Film Video For New Single 'The Devil In I'|publisher = Blabbermouth|date = 2014-08-05|accessdate = 2014-08-08|archive-date = 2014-08-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140811055249/http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/slipknot-to-film-video-for-new-single-the-devil-in-i/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/.5-gray-chapter-special-edition/id911121206/|title = ''.5: The Gray Chapter''|publisher = iTunes|date = 2014-08-24|accessdate = 2014-08-24|archive-date = 2014-09-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140905171007/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/.5-gray-chapter-special-edition/id911121206|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

10月17日，發行第五張專輯《灰五樂章》，再度登上告示牌200大專輯榜第1名<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.billboard.com/artist/279598/Slipknot/chart?f=305|title = Slipknot|publisher = billboard|accessdate = 2016-09-16|archive-date = 2019-05-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190525122001/https://www.billboard.com/artist/279598/Slipknot/chart?f=305|dead-url = no}}</ref>，在瑞士、加拿大、澳洲及日本的排行榜也登上第1名<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.swisscharts.com/album/Slipknot/.5:-The-Gray-Chapter-257906|title = Slipknot - .5: The Gray Chapter|publisher = Swiss Charts|accessdate = 2016-09-16|archive-date = 2021-04-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210417020506/http://swisscharts.com/album/Slipknot/.5:-The-Gray-Chapter-257906|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.billboard.com/artist/279598/Slipknot/chart?f=309|title = Slipknot|publisher = billboard|accessdate = 2016-09-16|archive-date = 2019-05-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190524144723/https://www.billboard.com/artist/279598/Slipknot/chart?f=309|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Slipknot&titel=.5%3A+The+Gray+Chapter&cat=a|title = SLIPKNOT - .5: THE GRAY CHAPTER (ALBUM)|publisher = ARIA Charts: Australias Official Music Charts|accessdate = 2016-09-16|archive-date = 2021-02-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210203194013/https://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Slipknot&titel=%2E5%3A+The+Gray+Chapter&cat=a|dead-url = no}}</ref>。10月25日，樂團展開新專輯的北美巡迴「Prepare for Hell Tour」，並二度舉辦Knotfest音樂節<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.metalinjection.net/tour-dates/knotfest-announce-new-bands-another-stage-added|title = KNOTFEST Announce New Bands & Another Stage Added|last = Pasbani|first = Robert|publisher = MetalInjection|date = 2014-08-11|accessdate = 2014-08-29|archive-date = 2014-09-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140904031114/http://www.metalinjection.net/tour-dates/knotfest-announce-new-bands-another-stage-added|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2015年初，參加澳洲的{{link-en|Soundwave音樂節|Soundwave (Australian music festival)}}<ref name="Soundwave 2015">{{cite web|language=en|last1=Childers|first1=Chad|title=Slipknot, Faith No More, Soundgarden, Slash + Many More Lead 2015 Soundwave Festival|url=http://loudwire.com/slipknot-faith-no-more-soundgarden-slash-2015-soundwave-festival/?fb123nc|website=Loudwire.com|publisher=Loudwire|accessdate=2014-08-21|archive-date=2014-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821225727/http://loudwire.com/slipknot-faith-no-more-soundgarden-slash-2015-soundwave-festival/?fb123nc|dead-url=no}}</ref>。貝斯與鼓的空缺則另外找了兩位神秘樂手客串，Crahan設計了新款面具讓他們戴上<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://loudwire.com/slipknot-corey-taylor-5-the-gray-chapter-2014-knotfest-more/|title = Slipknot's Corey Taylor Talks '.5: The Gray Chapter,' 2014 Knotfest + Moving Forward|last = Full Metal Jackie|first = Full Metal Jackie|publisher = Loudwire|date = 2014-09-10|accessdate = 2014-09-10|archive-date = 2021-01-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126221754/https://loudwire.com/slipknot-corey-taylor-5-the-gray-chapter-2014-knotfest-more/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。9月12日，發表〈The Devil in I〉的音樂錄影帶，除了Taylor戴著新面具，其他成員都戴著舊版面具，樂迷紛紛猜測鼓手與貝斯手的身分，但樂團始終沒有證實他們是誰<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/new-slipknot-bassists-identity-revealed/|title = New Slipknot Bassist's Identity Revealed? - Blabbermouth.net|publisher = ''Blabbermouth''|date = 2014-09-12|accessdate = 2014-09-13|archive-date = 2014-09-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140914213627/http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/new-slipknot-bassists-identity-revealed/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.rollingstone.com/music/videos/slipknot-host-asylum-rave-in-terrifying-the-devil-in-i-video-20140912|title = Slipknot Host Asylum Rave in Terrifying 'The Devil In I' Video|last = Kreps|first = Daniel|publisher = RollingStone|date = 2014-09-12|accessdate = 2014-09-19|archive-date = 2018-01-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180105123119/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/videos/slipknot-host-asylum-rave-in-terrifying-the-devil-in-i-video-20140912|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

因被拍到手上獨特的刺青，據樂迷稱那位貝斯手就是某位知名音樂人。Taylor後來說，保密貝斯手的身分是避免打亂計畫，他覺得自己很蠢 :「我當時想… 為什麼不給他戴個手套呢? 我給他蓋上頭巾、戴上面具，就是想要把他的刺青都蓋住。但是我忘記他的手也有刺青了」<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://loudwire.com/slipknot-corey-taylor-new-bassist-identity-leak-so-upset/|title = Slipknot's Corey Taylor on New Bassist's Identity Leak: 'I Was So Upset'|last = Hartmann|first = Graham|publisher = Loudwire|date = 2014-10-08|accessdate = 2014-10-08|archive-date = 2020-11-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201126163837/https://loudwire.com/slipknot-corey-taylor-new-bassist-identity-leak-so-upset/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="roxyrocker1">{{cite news|language=中文|url=http://www.roxyrocker.com/2014/12/04/%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%EF%BC%8Cslipknot-%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A/|title=感謝網友分享，Slipknot 新人身分確定|publisher=ROXY ROCKER 搖滾客|date=2014-12-04|accessdate=2016-09-16|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127065334/https://roxyrocker.com/2014/12/04/%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%EF%BC%8Cslipknot-%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Root也告訴《{{link-en|Guitar World|Guitar World}}》不會公布鼓手的身份，而且貝斯手和鼓手都不是樂團的正式成員，「說不定新人巡迴一年之後，就會發現我們的確是群瘋子而不願再合作，或者是我們就直接開除新鼓手。更何況Slipknot這群人都是男人中的男人，我們隨時都有可能發生衝突」<ref name="roxyrocker1"/><ref name="NewBassist">{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.metalinjection.net/latest-news/slipknots-corey-taylor-says-drummer-bassist-arent-official-band-members-just-yet|title = SLIPKNOT May Never Reveal The Identity of Their Drummer|last = Pasbani|first = Robert|date = 2014-10-09|accessdate = 2014-10-11|archive-date = 2019-05-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190530183913/https://metalinjection.net/latest-news/slipknots-corey-taylor-says-drummer-bassist-arent-official-band-members-just-yet|dead-url = no}}</ref>。12月3日，被Slipknot解雇的鼓技師Norm Costa在網路上張貼偷拍照，他洩漏了巡演成員名單，上面寫著新成員{{link-en|Alessandro Venturella|Alessandro Venturella}}和{{link-en|Jay Weinberg|Jay Weinberg}}的名字<ref name="metalinjection.net">{{cite web|language = en|url = http://www.metalinjection.net/gossip/slipknot-itinerary-leaks-confirming-drummer-identity-as-jay-weinberg|title = SLIPKNOT Itinerary Leaks Confirming Drummer Identity as Jay Weinberg|publisher = metalinjection|date = 2014-12-03|accessdate = 2016-09-16|archive-date = 2014-12-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141210035454/http://www.metalinjection.net/gossip/slipknot-itinerary-leaks-confirming-drummer-identity-as-jay-weinberg|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2015年3月11日，吉他手Thomson在家中和家人酒醉打架、後腦勺被刺傷送醫，傷勢嚴重，但沒有生命危險<ref>{{cite news |language = en|url=http://www.desmoinesregister.com/story/news/crime-and-courts/2015/03/11/report-says-drunken-brothers-injure-knife-fight/70143556/ |title=Slipknot guitarist injured in Clive knife fight |last=Elmer |first=MacKenzie |work={{link-en|The Des Moines Register|The Des Moines Register}} |publisher={{link-en|Gannett Company|Gannett Company}} |date=2015-03-12 |accessdate=2016-07-17 }}</ref>。8月2日，在[[康乃狄克州|康乃狄克州]]的一場演出中，新任貝斯手Venturella因嚴重脫水緊急送醫，20分鐘後，Slipknot還是繼續演出<ref name="XinMedia">{{cite news|language=中文|url=http://solomo.xinmedia.com/music/88709-Slipknot1103|title=Slipknot台灣演唱會公布舉辦日期與地點|publisher=XinMedia欣傳媒|date=2016-08-25|accessdate=2016-09-16|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926055147/https://solomo.xinmedia.com/music/88709-Slipknot1103|dead-url=no}}</ref>。對此Taylor表示：「因為他還不是Slipknot的一員」<ref>{{cite news|language=中文|url=http://www.roxyrocker.com/2015/08/12/corey-taylor-%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B%E6%96%B0%E5%9C%98%E5%93%A1%E9%82%84%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF-slipknot-%E4%B8%80%E5%93%A1/|title=COREY TAYLOR 解釋新團員還不是 Slipknot 一員|publisher=ROXY ROCKER 搖滾客|date=2015-08-12|accessdate=2016-09-16|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118063416/https://roxyrocker.com/2015/08/12/corey-taylor-%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B%E6%96%B0%E5%9C%98%E5%93%A1%E9%82%84%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF-slipknot-%E4%B8%80%E5%93%A1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月8日，Venturella康復回到舞台演出<ref name="XinMedia"/>。

=== 四度沉寂、新單曲及第六張錄音室專輯 (2017至今) ===
2017年，樂團主唱Corey Taylor忙於另一樂團Stone Sour的工作，其他團員則繼續創作新歌曲。

2018年8月28日，主唱Corey Taylor表示新專輯目前處於錄製DEMO階段，而新專輯將比第二張專輯"Iowa"還要重，他們希望能在2019年出，將剛好是樂團第一張專輯發佈的20周年。

10月31日，新單曲"All Out Life"發佈，Corey Taylor表示「新專輯正在進行中，它將會是Slipknot歷史上最黑暗的章節，新專輯有很重的旋律，很兇也表達憤怒卻相當真實，這真是太棒了，而且現在正在討論人們生活中需要做的很多事情。希望能在2019年出，將剛好是樂團第一張專輯發佈的20周年。」

== 特色 ==
=== 音樂風格和主題 ===
Slipknot的音樂受到許多硬搖滾和重金屬樂團的影響，如：[[Kiss合唱團|接吻樂團]]、[[炭疽熱樂團|炭疽熱樂團]]、[[黑色安息日|黑色安息日]]、[[鐵娘子樂團|鐵娘子]]、{{link-en|Faith No More|Faith No More}}、{{link-en|Helmet|Helmet (band)}}、{{link-en|Mr. Bungle|Mr. Bungle}}、[[工具樂隊|Tool]]、[[超級殺手|超級殺手]]、{{link-en|Fear Factory|Fear Factory}}、{{link-en|Skinny Puppy|Skinny Puppy}}、{{link-en|Neurosis|Neurosis (band)}}、[[猶大祭司|猶大祭司]]、[[齊柏林飛船|齊柏林飛船]]、[[金屬製品|金屬製品]]和[[野獸男孩|野獸男孩]]<ref>{{cite web|language=en|title=Slipknot Biography|work=Allmusic|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/slipknot-mn0000750742|accessdate=2017-03-14|archive-date=2013-06-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HOVoZyvv?url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/slipknot-mn0000750742|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AMG"/><ref name="BNW-book">{{cite book |language = en|last = Udo |first = Tommy |title = Brave Nu World |url = https://archive.org/details/bravenuworld00tomm|publisher=Sanctuary Publishing |year = 2002 |page = 第124頁 |isbn = 1-86074-415-X}}</ref><ref name="CD-book">{{cite book |last = Mudrian |language = en|first = Albert | title = Choosing Death:The Improbable History of Death Metal and Grindcore |publisher=Feral House |year = 2004 |page = 第258頁 |isbn = 1-932595-04-X}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en |author=Helmet |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/helmet-mn0000572737/related |title=Helmet | Similar Artists, Influenced By, Followers |publisher=AllMusic |accessdate=2014-04-23 |archive-date=2019-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190526071200/https://www.allmusic.com/artist/helmet-mn0000572737/related |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.mtv.com/artists/slipknot/related-artists/?filter=influencedBy |title=Slipknot Music Influences |website=MTV.com |publisher=MTV |access-date=2016-01-06 |archive-date=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206182844/http://www.mtv.com/artists/slipknot/related-artists/?filter=influencedBy |dead-url=no }}</ref>。媒體普遍將他們視為「美式重金屬新浪潮」的先驅之一。其成就經常被拿來與{{link-en|Pantera|Pantera}}、{{link-en|Machine Head|Machine Head (band)}}、{{link-en|Hatebreed|Hatebreed}}、{{link-en|Life of Agony|Life of Agony}}與{{link-en|Prong|Prong (band)}}比較<ref name="Blabbermouth">{{cite news |language=en |title='New Wave Of American Heavy Metal' Book Documents Over 600 Bands |url=http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=44955 |publisher=Blabbermouth.net |accessdate=2008-04-27 |archive-date=2008-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080521104002/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=44955 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

他們有時會被歸類為[[新金屬|新金屬]]<ref>{{cite magazine |language = en|url=http://www.stylusmagazine.com/feature.php?ID=1220 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20041009181930/http://www.stylusmagazine.com/feature.php?ID=1220 |title=Top Ten Nu-Metal Bands |magazine=Stylus magazine |date=2004-09-10 |last=Unterberger |first=Andrew |archivedate=2004-10-09 |accessdate=2014-09-25}}</ref>，樂團成員更樂於與其他新金屬樂團撇清關係，他們表示Slipknot和新金屬崛起只是時間上的巧合罷了<ref name="Rapcore1">{{cite book |language = en|author=Dick Porter|title = Rapcore: The Nu-Metal Rap Fusion |publisher=Plexus |location=London |page=第117頁 |year = 2003 |isbn = 0-85965-321-8}}</ref>。Slipknot的聲音相當凶狠彪悍，當中通常有降音的[[吉他定弦|吉他定弦]]、多重的打擊樂器聲、詭異的音效採樣和DJ刮盤聲<ref name="MFKR AMG">{{cite news |language = en|url = {{Allmusic|class=album|id=r524656|pure_url=yes}} |title = Allmusic Review of M.F.K.R. |accessdate = 2007-08-05 |publisher=Allmusic}}</ref>。採用多種聲音風格，人聲的典型特徵包括[[嘶吼唱腔|嘶吼唱腔]]、高聲咆哮，以及偶爾出現的旋律清腔<ref name="MFKR AMG"/>。樂團從成立開始便不斷在音樂上做實驗：最顯著的改變是第三張專輯中加入木吉他和旋律人聲<ref name="Vol. 3 AMG">{{cite news |language = en|url = {{Allmusic|class=album|id=r686871|pure_url=yes}} |title = Allmusic Review of Vol. 3 |accessdate = 2007-02-15 |last = Loftus |first = Johnny |publisher=allmusic}}</ref>。

他們的歌詞主題一般是具有侵略性的，包括褻瀆、社會批判、黑暗、[[虛無主義|虛無主義]]、憤怒、不滿、愛、厭世和精神病<ref name="AMG"/><ref name="Vol. 3 AMG"/>，也探討關於音樂產業、政治、紛爭和反思等主題<ref name="CoreyLyrics">{{cite magazine |language = en|title= Corey's All Hope Is Gone track by track |pages= 第6–7頁 |magazine=Kerrang! |date= 2008-07-19}}</ref>。美國音樂資料庫[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]的Rick Anderson表示：「這些歌詞顯然不適合闔家觀賞」<ref name="AMG1Album"/>。樂團的曲風含有[[蠱戮金屬|蠱戮金屬]]、[[死亡金屬|死亡金屬]]、[[工業金屬|工業金屬]]、[[鞭擊金屬|鞭擊金屬]]和{{link-en|驚悚搖滾|Shock rock}}的元素<ref name="yellmagazine">{{cite news|language=en |url=http://www.yellmagazine.com/slipknot-all-hope-is-gone/150/# |title=Slipknot: “All Hope Is Gone” & “Psychosocial” |accessdate=2016-09-16 |publisher=Yell! Magazine |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160122110233/http://www.yellmagazine.com/slipknot-all-hope-is-gone/150/ |archivedate=2016-01-22 }}</ref>，有時也被歸類為[[另類金屬|另類金屬]]<ref>{{cite web|language = en|last=Records |first=Roadrunner |url=http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/news/slipknot-announces-new-album-title |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111100814/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/news/slipknot-announces-new-album-title |archivedate=2014-01-11 |title=Slipknot Announces New Album Title! |publisher=Roadrunner Records |date=2011-07-12 |accessdate=2013-02-11}}</ref>。

=== 現場表演 ===
Slipknot以充滿暴戾、失控、瘋狂、怪異和混亂的現場演出聞名，這種原始而野性的風格也幫助樂團建立了人氣、迅速走向商業成功<ref name="AMG"/>。在演出中，大部分成員都會激烈甩頭、破壞物品、往台下人群跳水或直接打起架來<ref name="Rapcore1"/>。樂團早期的演出有許多極端行為，例如從2樓高的舞台跳下、成員間互相往身上點火<ref name="PGInt">{{cite video |language = en |date = 2010-06-06 |title = Our Last Interview with Paul Gray from Slipknot |url = http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9kq86-52hcU |medium = video |publisher = andPOP |accessdate = 2010-09-14 |time = 1:07 |archive-date = 2021-03-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309013440/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9kq86-52hcU |dead-url = no }}</ref>。近年來已減少這類激烈動作，已故貝斯手Gray生前曾表示，這是由於收到太多投訴，一來避免傷害他人，二來也能為這個"過動"的樂團延長壽命<ref name="PGInt"/>。除了充滿暴力和出乎預料的表演，他們也經常精心設計舞台效果，例如煙火、高架舞台、升降旋轉鼓座、液壓鼓式立管、輪式切割機和液晶螢幕<ref name="US2-2">{{cite news|language = en|last=Conner |first=Shea |title=Concert review: Slipknot at the Sprint Center with Coheed & Cambria and Trivium |publisher={{link-en|News-Press & Gazette Company|News-Press & Gazette Company}} |date=2009-01-26 |url=http://www.stjoenews.net/news/2009/jan/26/concert-review-slipknot-sprint-center-coheed-cambr/ |accessdate=2009-07-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090303225852/http://stjoenews.net/news/2009/jan/26/concert-review-slipknot-sprint-center-coheed-cambr/ |archivedate=2009-03-03 }}</ref>。搖滾雜誌《{{link-en|Kerrang!|Kerrang!}}》編輯Alistair Lawrence表示，Slipknot的現場是「一場精心編排的全面失控」<ref>{{cite magazine |language = en|title= Behold: the rebirth of a giant |magazine=Kerrang! |page= 第16頁 |publisher=Emap |date= 2008-12-06}}</ref>。雜誌《新音樂快遞》則簡短評論「亂成一團」<ref name="NMErev">{{cite news |language= en |title= Slipknot bring fire and destruction to Download |work= NME |date= 2009-06-14 |url= http://www.nme.com/news/slipknot/45333 |accessdate= 2009-06-16 |archive-date= 2009-06-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090616120741/http://www.nme.com/news/slipknot/45333 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

=== 形象 ===
[[File:Slipknot_@_Claremont_Showgrounds_(5_3_2012)_(7005619843).jpg|180px]]
Slipknot有著引人注目的招牌形象：設計精細、有著「德州電鋸殺人狂」風格的恐怖面具，類似囚衣的{{link-en|連身工作服|Jumpsuit}}、上面有成員各自的編號（0號到8號）及條碼。不過編碼的特色在Paul Gray逝世後已減少了<ref name="AMG"/>。

樂團曾表示，戴面具的想法來自Shawn Crahan在排練時戴的小丑面具<ref name="Arnopp40"/>。1997年底，樂團決定每個成員都穿戴獨特的面具和連身工作服<ref>Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第54-55頁</ref>。主唱Taylor後來針對他們的面具表示：「面具代表心中那個被噤聲的自我。就像是內心最想說的話、最想做的事情，它沒有辦法暢所欲言、隨心所欲。面具只是一種我們表現自己、與音樂親密的方式，沒那麼複雜」<ref>{{cite news|language=中文|url=http://www.roxyrocker.com/2014/12/02/slipknot-%E7%9A%84-corey-taylor-%E6%B7%BA%E8%AB%87%E3%80%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%85%B7%E3%80%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9%E5%9C%A8%E5%93%AA%EF%BC%9F/|title=Slipknot 的 Corey Taylor 淺談「面具」對自己的意義在哪？|publisher=ROXY ROCKER 搖滾客|date=2014-12-04|accessdate=2016-09-16|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115150242/https://roxyrocker.com/2014/12/02/slipknot-%E7%9A%84-corey-taylor-%E6%B7%BA%E8%AB%87%E3%80%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%85%B7%E3%80%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9%E5%9C%A8%E5%93%AA%EF%BC%9F/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。成員的編號、穿囚衣式連身工作服的概念，則是對音樂產業商業化的回應，Taylor表示：「原本我們只是想穿看看囚服...我們突然覺得，不如進一步把自己編個號碼，意思是告訴大家"嘿，我們是一個產品！"」<ref>Jason Arnopp《Slipknot: Inside the Sickness, Behind the Masks》(2001) ISBN 978-0091879334，第80頁</ref>。

樂團每個成員都有獨一無二的面具，他們也會在下一張新專輯發行時就更換面具的樣貌、更新連身服<ref name="IowaMasks">{{cite news |language = en |publisher = Blabbermouth.net |title = News Archive |date = 2001-05-20 |url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=119 |accessdate = 2007-12-16 |archive-date = 2008-06-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080620042927/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=119 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Vol3Masks">{{cite news |language = en |last = Wiederhorn |first = Jon |title = Slipknot Ready To Unveil New Masks, Subliminal |publisher = MTV |date = 2004-03-09 |url = http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1485648/20040309/slipknot.jhtml |accessdate = 2007-12-16 |archive-date = 2009-06-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090602051037/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1485648/20040309/slipknot.jhtml |dead-url = no }}</ref>。面具的外觀和風格通常不會改變太多，成員會各別確立自己的面具主題，每次增加一些新元素上去。Jordison表示：「面具的改變，表示每個人的成長」<ref name="MaskInterview">{{cite video |language = en|people = Chris Fehn, Joey Jordison, Corey Taylor |title = Slipknot – Ahoy Netherlands Interview |medium = Video |time = 0:44 |publisher=The Box |date = 2004}}</ref>。早期的面具是樂團自製，2000年後，已委由特效藝術家{{link-en|Screaming Mad George|Screaming Mad George}}訂製<ref name="MaskInterview2">{{cite video |language = en|title = Slipknot – Chris and Paul – Boogie TV Interview 2004 |medium = Video |publisher=Boogie TV |date = 2004}}</ref>。

樂團的形象一直飽受批評和爭議，批評人士通常指責他們是一個商業噱頭<ref>Joel McIver《Slipknot Unmasked (Again)》(2003) ISBN 978-0711997646，第32頁</ref>。樂團成員反對這些說法，他們表示面具可以讓聽眾的注意力聚集在音樂上，而不是在他們本人身上<ref name="LT">{{cite video |language = en|date = 2001 |title = Loud Times Video Magazine – Vol. 3 |medium = DVD |time=6:15 in Slipknot's interview. |publisher=Quantum Leap}}</ref>。主唱Taylor曾在演出中指著台下兩個崇拜者破口大罵「不要注意我們的外表！不要模仿我們，白痴！」。幾位成員也紛紛表示，戴面具幫他們保持了個人生活隱私。打擊樂手Fehn表示「面具是一種祝福，它意味著我們不需要社會公眾的認可」<ref>{{cite news |language = en |publisher = Blabbermouth.net |title = Slipknot's Chris Fehn: 'It's A Blessing That We Don't Get Recognized' |date = 2005-05-25 |url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=36072 |accessdate = 2010-09-11 |archive-date = 2005-05-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20050508073339/http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=36072 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。2012年，樂團在iOS和Android平台上發表了「Slipknot: Wear the Mask」應用程式，邀請樂迷製作自己的面具，並分類自己是哪一類型的樂迷<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/culture/blogs/gear-up/slipknot-app-lets-fans-wear-the-mask-20120724|title=Slipknot App Lets Fans 'Wear the Mask'|first=Joe|last=Pinsker|work=Rolling Stone|access-date=2016-09-16|archive-date=2014-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140123032718/http://www.rollingstone.com/culture/blogs/gear-up/slipknot-app-lets-fans-wear-the-mask-20120724|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

